text: Jill Eikenberry (born 21 January 1947) is an American actress. She was born in New Haven, Connecticut. Her most well known role was playing Ann Kelsey in L.A. Law (1986-1994). She appeared in many television movies in the 1980s. == Other websites == * Category:1947 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from New Haven, Connecticut Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:American television actors
